== Lyrics ==
The [[Urdu]] lyrics, written by the Pakistani Urdu-language poet, Hafeez Jullundhri in 1952, have commonality with [[Persian language|Persian]], making them understandable in both languages.  No verse in the three stanza lyrics is repeated.<ref name="infopak1"/>
